{
  "stem": "56.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they took my aunt and my cousins the same day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took whoever they wanted, and-- No.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took whoever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took a lot of people beside the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So That was-- thank you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was the first action I was in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Then we just picked up our lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother was gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's nothing we could have done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My sister tried-- she tried to go to the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She tried to-- but no one could do nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother wore a sweater that my sister knitted for her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a very unusual, beautiful sweater.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a few days later, we got the sweater back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we just-- just kept on going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Life just went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were other problems.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My brother got sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we just did the best we could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we-- came the spring, the summer, we had some greenery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had something to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Prior to that, we used to go out and pick whatever we thought was edible, including, we found out that poison ivy, the European kind of poison ivy, is edible once it's cooked.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we used to go into the fields and pick that and eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were other little things that grew that could have been eaten.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We just-- whatever there was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We used to get a ration of so-called coffee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It consisted of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was barley, burned barley.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course, it was burned black.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But once you boiled it, the water would turn black, that was our coffee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we ate the barley that was left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, it was terrible, because it had the husks on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
